				\begin{document}$$^3$$\end{document}3RD model to be able to analyze a policy to reduce the number of infected individuals by the widespread introduction of tracing apps. These apps allow to break infection chains by sending infected individuals to quarantine (Q) before they can spread the virus further. Here, we assume that a fraction \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
