				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R_0$$\end{document}R0 is somewhere between 2 and 3; see the report29 by the European Center for Disease Control.

Typical estimates are 3 (reported in1), 2.3 (reported in2) or 2.26 (reported in28). For Germany, the Robert Koch-Institut (RKI) estimated \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
