Dynamics of the COVID-19 epidemic for the B2 (left) and the USD2 (right) scenario: susceptible individuals in green, recovered in blue, and aggregated asymptomatic, symptomatic, and severely infectious cases in orange. The group with low vulnerability has dotted curves, the group with high vulnerability is plotted solidly.

