				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R \approx 0.6$$\end{document}R≈0.6 generated from these interactions only. GSD2 also restricts all interactions involving the highly vulnerable population to \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
