				\begin{document}$$80\%$$\end{document}80%) compliance. (bottom-left): Changing Compliance in GSD3. Panel (bottom-right): Changing the Asymptomatic Rate in GSD3 with high (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
